{"tid":2424080,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【從數據認識經濟】一項數據看出庫房有幾缺水，交通違例收入五年增近八成","createTime":"2021-02-26T09:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T11:07:03.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"683eaeb90aa4a4470848c13f990d18341b81bb8c","tid":2424080,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gAWPduDLhALwbhFaP85TSQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/5O88hX4b.qMaO4CwDhsMyg--~B/aD0xMjAwO3c9MTIwMDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/business_digest_949/e192ed6d69c29c21bae701446de8437a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FgAWPduDLhALwbhFaP85TSQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F5O88hX4b.qMaO4CwDhsMyg--~B%2FaD0xMjAwO3c9MTIwMDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fbusiness_digest_949%2Fe192ed6d69c29c21bae701446de8437a&h=065c8971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府於早前已經預告今年財赤數字將大超預期，但其實有一項數字都可以直接看到政府庫房有幾缺水。據近日公布的《財政預算案》，交通違例事項的定額罰款制度（俗稱「牛肉乾」）收入增至6.48億，較2014/15年度增加約78%。<br />\n<br />\n2018/19年度的「罰款、沒收及罰金」修訂預算20.73億元，較原來預算的14.35億元，增加約44.5%，佔政府該年度收入總額的0.4%，其中，交通違例收入達6.48億元。運輸及房屋局於今年1月提交立法會的答覆文件顯示，去年發出超過201萬張「牛肉乾」。所以，網上流傳「如果看到經常見到抄牌，證明庫房很等錢」，這一句可能是真的。<br />\n<br />\n6.48億元的交通違例收入，到底是一個什麼概念？<br />\n<br />\n目前，俗稱「牛肉乾」違例泊車定額罰款額為320元，6.48億即是共發出了202,500張「牛肉乾」。按一年365日計算，每日約發出5547張，每小時發出約231張，每分鐘則發出約3.8張。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：財政預算案"},{"pid":"3e7533d198c7cee1b9cc233da2e7b11280b37216","tid":2424080,"uid":357710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"683eaeb90aa4a4470848c13f990d18341b81bb8c","tid":2424080,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gAWPduDLhALwbhFaP85TSQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/